parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to stall or shut off while driving, leading to a loss of power steering and brakes, which can increase the risk of accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or shuts off while driving
the engine turns off without warning
the key has to be forcefully pushed into the ignition
the ignition switch catches or hesitates
the vehicle has difficulty starting
and the dashboard lights may flicker or go out.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or shut off while driving, leading to a loss of power steering and brakes, which can increase the risk of accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or shuts off while driving
the engine turns off without warning
the dashboard lights may flicker or go out
the horn may not work
the cruise control may not function
and the interior lights may not turn on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or jerk, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips
hesitates
or jerks when shifting gears
especially when accelerating from a stop or merging into traffic. The vehicle may lose power
stall
or refuse to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling or failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to a loss of control, accidents, or strand the driver.
symptoms: The engine suddenly shuts off
stalls
or fails to start; the vehicle loses power while driving; the check engine light illuminates; the vehicle may restart after a few minutes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the engine to stall or fail, leading to a loss of control, accidents, or strand the driver.
symptoms: The engine stalls or fails to start; the vehicle loses power while driving; the check engine light illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the EGR valve can cause the engine to stall or fail, leading to a loss of control, accidents, or strand the driver.
symptoms: The engine stalls or fails to start; the vehicle loses power while driving; the check engine light illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the catalytic converter can cause the engine to stall or fail, leading to a loss of control, accidents, or strand the driver.
symptoms: The check engine light illuminates; the vehicle fails emissions testing; the engine stalls or fails to start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the EVAP system can cause the engine to stall or fail, leading to a loss of control, accidents, or strand the driver.
symptoms: The check engine light illuminates; the vehicle fails emissions testing; the engine stalls or fails to start.
